<item>
            <title>[LU-15176] Encrypted directory cannot be mounted as subdirectory</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15176</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Doing subdirectory mount for an encrypted directory fails, because Lustre is not able to retrieve the encryption context of the root inode of the filesystem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will push a patch to address this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
